item.title: Working Group on NIH DMSP Guidance
item.description: About This working group is a community effort to create resources to share with the researcher community in regards to the NIH Data Management and Sharing Policy (2023). Materials, the list of contributors, and more can be found at the project website on OSF. Acknowledgments This project was made possible with support from the RDAP Association. The content is solely the responsibility of the authors and does not necessarily represent the official views of the RDAP association.
